{
  "signal_description": "Retrieve the 'Document Type', 'Payment Time', and 'No. of Invoices' from the 'defaultview-529' table. The 'Document Type' is the average time it takes for an invoice to be cleared after it is created. The 'Payment Time' is calculated by subtracting the first 'END_TIME' of the 'Create Invoice' event from the last 'END_TIME' of the 'Clear Invoice' event. The 'No. of Invoices' is the count of 'case_id' where the 'Last Inv. Item Due Date' is less than the 'Last Inv. Item Clearing Date'. The results are ordered by the 'Payment Time' in descending order. Only records with a non-null 'Payment Time' are selected."
}
